# Alawein Governance Rule

When working in `alawein/alawein`:

1. Keep governance docs aligned (`AGENTS.md`, `CLAUDE.md`, `SSOT.md`, and docs under `docs/governance/`).
2. Before suggesting a commit or PR, run:
   - `python scripts/sync-readme.py --check`
   - `./scripts/validate-doc-contract.sh --full`
3. Treat [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) and [docs/governance](../../docs/governance/) as authoritative boundaries for this repo.
4. Do not skip required governance validations for managed docs.

